### List Subscription Plans (Public/Static info usually, but here we create one)
# Admin creates a plan logic is usually backend config, but user subscribes:

### Create Subscription (Student)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "plan": "premium",
    "start_date": "2025-01-01",
    "end_date": "2025-02-01",
    "package_type": "all_in_one",
    "duration": 1,
    "duration_unit": "months",
    "price": 150000,
    "auto_renew": false
}

### Create Transaction for Course (Student)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions/courses/1
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "payment_method": "qris"
}

### List My Transactions (Student)
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Accept: application/json
